<paragraph id="4CBEFB21745B6355193A9147F25D1025" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
(Figure 
<figureCitation id="9F4ADB342A3D747E4D7A4CCBE256F0D1" captionStart="Figure 33" captionStartId="F33" captionText="Figure 33. Distribution of Solanum palitans in its non-native range in the Old World." figureDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.106.21991.figure33" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/218736" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">33</figureCitation>
